        "creation_date": 1571055260,
        "body": "<p>Default scope of an entity is Singleton - Here only one instance of your bean will be created and that will be returned in every subsequent request call.<\/p>\n\n<p>In case of Prototype scope, new bean instance will be created for each request to that bean. <\/p>\n",
